    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash the <strong>rocket</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Fluff the <strong>drained bulgur wheat </strong>with a fork then add the <strong>sultanas</strong>, <strong>rocket</strong> and 1 tbsp<strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </strong>[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>honey-thyme dressing</strong> and gently mix – this is your <strong>bulgur salad</strong></p>",
